---
title: BBQ Pork and Apple Meatballs with Creamy Mashed Potatoes and Side Salad
description: Grab some extra napkins because things are about to get saucy! These juicy meatballs are smothered in sweet and savoury BBQ sauce. Served with creamy mashed potatoes, crispy shallots and a fresh salad, this meal has got it all.
